@startuml Component Diagram - Layer 3: Domain Services (Simplified)
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/plantuml-stdlib/C4-PlantUML/master/C4_Component.puml
title Layer 3: Domain Services (Thin IPC Wrappers - Business Logic in Node.js)

Container_Boundary(renderer, "Renderer Process (Angular)") {

    Component(nav_service, "Navigation Service", "IPC Coordinator", "→ Angular Router → update nav_state")
    
    Component(import_service, "Import Service", "IPC Coordinator", "→ IPC: loadDIP command → update import_state → manage: retry, progress")
    
    Component(search_service, "Search Service", "IPC Coordinator", "→ IPC: query command → update search_state → manage: validation, cache")
    
    Component(verification_service, "Verification Service", "IPC Coordinator", "→ IPC: verify command → manage: UI feedback")
    
    Component(export_service, "Export Service", "IPC Coordinator", "→ IPC: export command → manage: format selection")
    
    Component(metadata_service, "Metadata Service", "IPC Coordinator", "→ IPC: getMetadata command → manage: caching")
}

Container_Boundary(main, "Main Process (Node.js)") {
    Component(backend, "Business Logic", "Where work happens", "✓ Search algorithms ✓ Indexing ✓ Verification ✓ File I/O ✓ AI embeddings")
}

Rel(nav_service, backend, "Commands via IPC")
Rel(import_service, backend, "Commands via IPC")
Rel(search_service, backend, "Commands via IPC")
Rel(verification_service, backend, "Commands via IPC")
Rel(export_service, backend, "Commands via IPC")
Rel(metadata_service, backend, "Commands via IPC")

note as domain_services
  **Layer 3: Domain Services**
  
  Thin Wrapper Pattern:
  Each service:
  ✓ Coordinates one business capability
  ✓ Sends IPC commands to Main Process
  ✓ Receives responses
  ✓ Updates local state observable
  ✓ Manages local UI/retry logic
  ✗ Never executes algorithms
  ✗ Never touches database
  ✗ Never performs complex computations
  
  Principle: Single Responsibility
  - NavigationService = routing only
  - ImportService = load coordination only
  - SearchService = query coordination only
  - VerificationService = verify coordination only
  - ExportService = export coordination only
  - MetadataService = metadata coordination only
  
  Architecture: Command/Response Pattern
  Component → Service.method()
       ↓
  Service sends IPC command
       ↓
  Main Process executes
       ↓  
  IPC response received
       ↓
  Service updates state
       ↓
  Component receives update
end note

@enduml
